> Dear AnAnomalousWriter:
>
> I deeply apologize for the fact that the second half as you are seeing it is currently severely unfinished. The formatting of it has proven to be very, very challenging and due to circumstances regarding how I write I severely underestimated the length of time it would take to complete the CSS. That being said, I am working on it diligently and will update this page when I can with the rest of the article. I have also included a rough numbered version of the plot should you want to finish the story before I am able to finish the rest. Again, I deeply apologize for giving you what is essentially a pot with no handles. It was not my intention and I hope you will enjoy what there is so far.
> 
> Happy Holidays,
> Your friend JackalRelated
